ACE Permission Setup (server.cfg)

Add this to server.cfg

add_ace group.leo sisler.dui.leo allow
add_ace group.civ sisler.dui.civ allow

Example assigning a player:

add_principal identifier.license:YOUR_LICENSE_HERE group.leo
 Commands
Civilians simulate drinking
/drink 0.05
/drink 0.12
Police breathalyze /breathalyze

Example result:

Breathalyzer Result
BAC: 0.11 | DUI: YES

